Safety & Information,Vehicle Information,Information procedures,Locating vehicle information ,The Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) is a 17-character identification composed of letters and digits. This number is unique throughout the world. The objective of this procedure is to show you how to understand the principles of vehicle identification numbers and correctly identify the components that make up a vehicle identification number.,Procedure,locatevin_2.html,locatevin_pc.html,,,locatevin_WS_2.pdf,HA121_2.pdf
