Safety & Information,Vehicle Configurations,Vehicle inspection procedures,Measuring a wheelbase ,The wheelbase is the distance between the center of the front wheel and the center of the rear wheel and is normally the same on both sides of the vehicle. The objective of this procedure is to show you how to identify and measure the wheelbase.,Procedure,measwhlbase_2.html,measwhlbase_pc.html,,,measwhlbase_WS_2.pdf,HA097_2.pdf
