Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Clutches,Multi-plate clutches ,"Increasing the number of plates in a friction clutch unit, increases its torque capacity.",Theory,multiclutch_2.html,multiclutch_pc.html,multiclutch_kc.html,,,HA573_2.pdf
Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Clutches,Operating mechanisms,"The clutch operating mechanism may be mechanical or hydraulic. When the clutch pedal is depressed, the movement is relayed to a release fork which carries the release bearing.",Theory,operatingmechanisms_2.html,operatingmechanisms_pc.html,operatingmechanisms_kc.html,,,HA575_2.pdf
Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Gearbox layout & operation ,Gearbox layouts ,"In a manual transmission for a rear-wheel drive vehicle, the gear train is built up on three shafts: the input shaft, the countershaft, and the main shaft.",Theory,gearboxlayout_2.html,gearboxlayout_pc.html,gearboxlayout_kc.html,,,HA584_2.pdf
Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Gearbox layout & operation ,Transaxle designs ,"In transaxle designs, the drive is transferred through the clutch unit to a primary shaft. The primary shaft carries gears of different sizes which mesh with gears on a secondary shaft.",Theory,transaxledesign_2.html,transaxledesign_pc.html,transaxledesign_kc.html,,,HA585_2.pdf
Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Clutches & manual transmissions procedures,Checking gearbox oil ,Correct fluid level is critical to effective and efficient operation. The objective of this procedure is to show you how to check the lubricant level of a transaxle and final drive.,Procedure,chkgearboxoil_2.html,chkgearboxoil_pc.html,,,chkgearboxoil_WS_2.pdf,HA589_2.pdf
Transmissions,Clutches & Manual Transmissions,Clutches & manual transmissions procedures,Changing manual gearbox oil ,"The objective of this procedure is to show you how to change the lubricant in a manual gearbox or transaxle. When preparing to drain the lubricant, warm up the transmission fluid by idling or driving the vehicle.",Procedure,changegearboxoil_2.html,changegearboxoil_pc.html,,,changegearboxoil_WS_2.pdf,HA590_2.pdf
